            <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
                <img src="http://placehold.it/250x250&text=Hello world" height="200px" width="200px">
                <h3>Personalised Analysis</h3>
                <p>Analyse your Dota games and compare to top players. See the patterns in your play from last hitting performance to fights. </p>
            </div> 
            <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
                <img src="http://placehold.it/250x250&text=Hello world" height="200px" width="200px">
